{"tid":2490040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「娛賓」女記者遭警暴反被控拒捕 兩警口供故意不提曾使用胡椒噴霧","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T11:29:03.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a7bbcb153292277bba7cabe0ab89da815edeca55","tid":2490040,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:06:23.000Z","msg":"網媒「娛賓」一名女記者去年母親節深夜採訪期間，在公園公廁疑遭防暴警施用暴力，包括跪頸及以胡椒噴霧「噴完一支又一支」，女記者一度休克及失禁，最終反被控抗拒警員執行職務，案件今日續審。有份制服被告的警員，其<span class=\"red\">證人口供紙沒有記錄施放胡椒噴霧一事</span>，被辯方質疑刻意隱瞞。惟不論辯方問警員是否「特登唔提」、「選擇唔提」以及「點解唔提」，警員均重複回答謂<span class=\"red\">「我冇落到」</span>。主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">嚴舜儀裁定案件表證成立</span>，押後至明天續審，屆時被告會決定是否自辯。<br />\n<br />\n警長擔心同袍遇襲，故在警長命令下到醫院戒備。辯方質疑警方其實因自知闖禍，感到擔心，故到醫院了解被告傷勢。李稱不同意。<br />\n<br />\n辯方爭議李刻意隱瞞警方使用暴力一事，李答沒刻意隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官嚴舜儀裁定案件表證成立，押後至明天續審，屆時被告會決定是否自辯。<span class=\"red\">辯方另會再傳召一名證人</span>。"},{"pid":"28bc6a4389763bdca038396cccebb41d9d813a76","tid":2490040,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/4RN7IYSCHNBF5OLUXR52M3FRUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2F4RN7IYSCHNBF5OLUXR52M3FRUA%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=548c58d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2F4RN7IYSCHNBF5OLUXR52M3FRUA%2F&h=fb1a5124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/4RN7IYSCHNBF5OLUXR52M3FRUA/</a>"},{"pid":"50a08afe4cc1a004be5fae4da7ccb649789bcd9b","tid":2490040,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:11:20.000Z","msg":"香港精英"},{"pid":"fe7fbffffc03aba5c1af83a54a84766ccf090b38","tid":2490040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/